      <title>亿万富翁萨德的妻子掌管不断扩张的媒体帝国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/billionaire-saade-s-wife-takes-charge-of-expanding-media-empire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国亿万富翁萨德家族四十多年来一直严格控制着企业运营。随着家族子孙罗道夫·萨德的妻子掌管迅速扩张的媒体部门，这种做法在第二代中愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/billionaire-saade-s-wife-takes-charge-of-expanding-media-empire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
