    <item>
      <title>马赫卢夫称尚不清楚欧洲央行将以多快的速度继续行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/makhlouf-says-it-s-unclear-how-fast-ecb-will-carry-on-if-at-all</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员加布里埃尔·马赫卢夫表示，由于通胀前景仍不确定，目前尚不清楚欧洲央行何时会再次降低利率——或者是否会降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/makhlouf-says-it-s-unclear-how-fast-ecb-will-carry-on-if-at-all</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 07:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通指数发布日期临近，印度储备创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-s-reserves-hit-record-as-jpmorgan-index-date-draws-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于外国投资者在印度债券被纳入摩根大通旗舰新兴市场债务指数前纷纷买入印度债券，印度的外汇储备上周增至 6515 亿美元的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-s-reserves-hit-record-as-jpmorgan-index-date-draws-near</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 06:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员警告不要急于进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员对未来降息的可能性做出了谨慎的评估，其中一位官员甚至表示，不会再次采取降息举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 05:44:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券持有人就瑞士信贷 AT1 债券在美国起诉瑞士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bondholders-sue-switzerland-in-us-over-credit-suisse-at1-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团在瑞士政府的斡旋下拯救了瑞士信贷集团，导致该银行的债券投资者损失惨重。现在，他们正在纽约对瑞士提起诉讼，并将诉讼范围扩大到国外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bondholders-sue-switzerland-in-us-over-credit-suisse-at1-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:33:52 GMT</pubDate>
